content: Hi <@1266900496770400339>. Thanks for being here with us tonight. We're glad you're using Reach. Thanks for the suggestion. You'll find a few of the battleground states have their own Galleries in Reach's Library. I know the team is hard at work updating Reach, so your patience is appreciated as we get it all up to speed. Again, thanks for volunteering!

Thanks... I hadn't noticed the extra Galleries:) 
Still learning, but loving how easy it is to share!

Fantastic! Oh, I understand. It takes a little time to explore it. FYI: Reach is also available as a website. For this just navigate to https://www.reach.vote/ in your favorite browser and sign in using the same e-mail you have used to register your account. Thanks again for volunteering!
